# This is the EcoEase Documentation for Machine Learning API Classification

Long short story, EcoEase is one of Bangkit 2023 Capstone projects which focuses on a waste issue around us. We try to eliminate this issue by providing an app 
that can classify garbage type and call "garbage collector" to help the user to cleanup their waste.

## List APi

### **Garbage Classification**

| Usage    | Endpoint                         |
| -------- | -------------------------------- |
| Classify | POST http://ecoease.api/classify |

**parameters**

| Parameter    | Required | Deskripsi               |
| ------------ | -------- | ----------------------- |
| image    | Yes      | Foto sampah     |

**result**

```json
{
    "image_hex": "",
    "predicted_label": "plastic"
}
```
